=============================================
|ID|OPERATOR                       |NAME    |
---------------------------------------------
|0 |SCALAR GROUP BY                |        |
|1 |└─PX COORDINATOR               |        |
|2 |  └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR         |:EX10000|
|3 |    └─MERGE GROUP BY           |        |
|4 |      └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN       |        |
|5 |        ├─PX PARTITION ITERATOR|        |
|6 |        │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |b       |
|7 |        └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET|a       |
=============================================
